public class CarrotAwsCloudFormCreate
extends CarrotAwsCloudForm

cloud formation: create stack based on: stack name, stack template (stackTemplateFile), stack parameters (stackPropertiesInputFile + stackInputParams), and produce a stack output (stackPropertiesOutputFile) ; wait for completion or fail (CarrotAwsCloudForm.stackTimeout)
